by GrahamCampbell at 2014-11-17T22:48:00Z

I'm also experinencing issues with foreach loops:

```php
$var = [];
foreach ($foo as $i => $bar) {
    $var[] = [$i => $bar];
}
```
ends up as:
```php
$var = [];
foreach ($foo as $i => $bar) {
    $var[] = [$i    => $bar];
}
```

I don't know if this fixes that. Might be useful to add to the test suite.

